A father and daughter singing a duet from Disney hit Frozen has gone  viral with nearly 20 million views in just three days.

The clip of Chris Price, 26, from Leicester, and his four-year-old daughter Lily belting out 'Let it Go' has more than 850,000 likes and thousands of users have commented on his page. 

The 84-second clip shows the pair singing the popular Disney tune while driving to the shops for a day out in London.  

Lily sits in a car seat at the front and says she wants to sing 'super loud' as Chris puts the music on, asking 'is that loud enough?'

As she sings at the top of her lungs, little Lily stretches her arms wide in true diva style.  

